race.description: Bishop Collins Chartered Accountants Midway Handicap (C1)
race.comment: SPICE BABY (6) progressive Kembla Grange-trained filly with her hoof on the till. Gripped on late in a fast run contest when a narrow third over 1200m at Wyong. Key jockey change and has the speed to get across from the sticky gate. Go close. MATCHSTICKS (10) deep into her prep now and gets map favours here. Worked hard early from the outside gate when a tiring second over 1200m at Kembla Grange. Finds an easier contest and will prove tough to beat. CAPTIVATING TYCOON (2) bounced off his narrow debut fourth, with a dominant Maiden win 1000m at Kembla Grange. Will appreciate the rise in trip and will be attacking the line late. LEANTOTHEMOON (1) unlucky not to have a few more wins on the CV and ticks plenty of boxes for this. Key jockey change today after launching late for a sound second over 1100m at Hawkesbury. Stalks the speed and no surprise to see her take this out.
